<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.5">
<l>paṟṟār naṭuṅkamuṉ pāñcacaṉ ṉiyattai vāyvaitta pōrēṟē yeṉ</l>
<l>ciṟṟāyar ciṅkamē cītai maṇāḷā ciṟukkuṭṭac ceṅkaṇ mālē</l>
<l>ciṟṟāṭai yumciṟup pattira mumivai kaṭṭiliṉ mēlvait tuppōy</l>
<l>kaṟṟāya rōṭunī kaṉṟukaḷ mēyttuk kalantuṭaṉ vantāy pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Battle bull who placed [your] lips to Pāñcajanya long ago</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [your] enemies trembled!</l>
<l>My little lion of the herders! Bridegroom of Sītā!</l>
<l rend="indent">Little Boy! Red eyed Māl!</l>
<l>Having placed [your] little garment and toy dagger on [your] cot and left,</l>
<l>It seems you went off with the calf-herders to graze the calves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
